<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title><%= ENV['WEBSITE_NAME'] %> – Carpet Cleaning Software</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />

  <style>
    /* ===== <%= ENV['WEBSITE_NAME'] %> – Carpet Cleaning Software ===== */

    .cp-page {
      --bg: #f5f5fb;
      --bg-card: #ffffff;
      --text-main: #111827;
      --text-sub: #4b5563;
      --muted: #6b7280;
      --border-soft: #e5e7eb;
      --accent: #4f46e5;
      --accent-dark: #312e81;
      --accent-soft: #eef2ff;
      --accent-secondary: #f97316;
      --radius-lg: 20px;
      --radius-md: 16px;
      --radius-pill: 999px;
      --shadow-soft: 0 18px 45px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.16);

      font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
      color: var(--text-main);
      background: radial-gradient(circle at top left, #eef2ff 0, #f9fafb 40%, #f3f4f6 100%);
      padding: 40px 16px 80px;
    }

    .cp-page * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    .cp-shell {
      max-width: 1120px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    /* ---------- HERO ---------- */

    .cp-hero {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.4fr) minmax(0, 1fr);
      gap: 40px;
      align-items: center;
      margin-top: 32px;
      margin-bottom: 56px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .cp-hero {
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
      }
    }

    .cp-kicker {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      padding: 6px 12px;
      border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
      border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.6);
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #ffffff, #eef2ff);
      font-size: 12px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.11em;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .cp-kicker-dot {
      width: 8px;
      height: 8px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at center, #a5b4fc 0, #4f46e5 55%, #1e1b4b 100%);
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(129, 140, 248, 0.9);
    }

    .cp-title {
      font-size: clamp(32px, 4.4vw, 42px);
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: -0.035em;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .cp-title span {
      color: var(--accent-dark);
    }

    .cp-sub {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: var(--text-sub);
      max-width: 560px;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    .cp-hero-tagline {
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--accent-dark);
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .cp-hero-ctas {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    .cp-btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 10px 22px;
      border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 500;
      text-decoration: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      border: 1px solid transparent;
      white-space: nowrap;
      transition:
        transform 0.12s ease,
        box-shadow 0.15s ease,
        background 0.15s ease,
        border-color 0.15s ease,
        color 0.15s ease;
    }

    .cp-btn-primary {
      background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--accent), #6366f1);
      color: #ffffff;
      box-shadow: 0 14px 32px rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.45);
      border-color: rgba(191, 219, 254, 0.9);
    }

    .cp-btn-primary:hover {
      transform: translateY(-1px);
      box-shadow: 0 20px 44px rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.65);
    }

    .cp-btn-secondary {
      background: #ffffff;
      color: var(--accent-dark);
      border-color: rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.8);
    }

    .cp-btn-secondary:hover {
      background: #f3f4ff;
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }

    .cp-hero-trust {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--muted);
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 10px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .cp-hero-trust strong {
      color: var(--accent-dark);
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .cp-pill {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 4px;
      padding: 4px 8px;
      border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
      background: rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.06);
      color: #4b5563;
      border: 1px solid rgba(191, 219, 254, 0.9);
      font-size: 11px;
    }

    /* Hero right: job board mock */

    .cp-hero-media {
      position: relative;
    }

    .cp-board {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 360px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
      background: #0b1020;
      color: #e5e7eb;
      padding: 16px 16px 14px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-soft);
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .cp-board::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.9), transparent 65%);
      opacity: 0.9;
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .cp-board-inner {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      font-size: 12px;
    }

    .cp-board-header {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .cp-board-header-title {
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .cp-board-header-title span {
      display: block;
      font-size: 10px;
      color: #9ca3af;
    }

    .cp-board-filter {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 4px;
      padding: 3px 8px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.9);
      border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.7);
      font-size: 10px;
    }

    .cp-board-list {
      margin-top: 6px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.96);
      padding: 8px 10px;
    }

    .cp-board-row {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.3fr 0.8fr 0.7fr;
      gap: 4px;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 4px 0;
      font-size: 11px;
    }

    .cp-board-row + .cp-board-row {
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.4);
      margin-top: 3px;
      padding-top: 5px;
    }

    .cp-board-row strong {
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .cp-status-pill {
      padding: 2px 6px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-size: 10px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .cp-status-pill.booked {
      background: rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.25);
      color: #fed7aa;
    }

    .cp-status-pill.cleaning {
      background: rgba(22, 163, 74, 0.25);
      color: #bbf7d0;
    }

    .cp-status-pill.completed {
      background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.25);
      color: #bfdbfe;
    }

    .cp-board-footer {
      margin-top: 8px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      font-size: 10px;
      color: #cbd5f5;
    }

    .cp-board-footer strong {
      color: #e5e7eb;
    }

    /* ---------- SECTION LAYOUT ---------- */

    .cp-section {
      margin-bottom: 52px;
    }

    .cp-section-header {
      max-width: 780px;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    .cp-section-kicker {
      font-size: 12px;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .cp-section-title {
      font-size: 22px;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .cp-section-lead {
      font-size: 15px;
      color: var(--text-sub);
    }

    .cp-section-lead strong {
      color: var(--accent-dark);
    }

    .cp-body-text {
      font-size: 15px;
      color: var(--text-sub);
      line-height: 1.7;
      max-width: 760px;
    }

    .cp-body-text p {
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .cp-body-text p:last-child {
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    /* ---------- FEATURES GRID ---------- */

    .cp-feature-intro {
      max-width: 720px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .cp-feature-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 20px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 960px) {
      .cp-feature-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 720px) {
      .cp-feature-grid {
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
      }
    }

    .cp-feature-card {
      background: var(--bg-card);
      border-radius: var(--radius-md);
      border: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
      padding: 16px 16px 18px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 26px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.04);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 6px;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .cp-feature-label {
      font-size: 11px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .cp-feature-title {
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .cp-feature-text {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--text-sub);
    }

    .cp-feature-pill {
      margin-top: 4px;
      align-self: flex-start;
      padding: 4px 9px;
      border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
      font-size: 11px;
      background: var(--accent-soft);
      color: var(--accent-dark);
    }

    /* ---------- TESTIMONIALS ---------- */

    .cp-testimonial-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 20px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 800px) {
      .cp-testimonial-grid {
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
      }
    }

    .cp-testimonial-card {
      background: #0b1020;
      border-radius: var(--radius-md);
      padding: 18px 18px 16px;
      color: #e5e7eb;
      box-shadow: 0 16px 40px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.7);
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .cp-testimonial-card::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.6), transparent 60%);
      opacity: 0.95;
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .cp-testimonial-inner {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .cp-testimonial-tag {
      font-size: 11px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      color: #9ca3af;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .cp-testimonial-quote {
      font-size: 14px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      color: #e5e7eb;
    }

    .cp-testimonial-quote em {
      font-style: italic;
    }

    .cp-testimonial-name {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #9ca3af;
    }

    .cp-testimonial-name strong {
      display: block;
      color: #e5e7eb;
    }

    /* ---------- ARTICLES / RESOURCES ---------- */

    .cp-articles-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 20px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 960px) {
      .cp-articles-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 720px) {
      .cp-articles-grid {
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
      }
    }

    .cp-article-card {
      background: var(--bg-card);
      border-radius: 14px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
      padding: 14px 14px 16px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 6px;
      font-size: 13px;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.04);
    }

    .cp-article-tag {
      font-size: 11px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .cp-article-title {
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .cp-article-text {
      color: var(--text-sub);
    }

    .cp-article-meta {
      font-size: 11px;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .cp-article-link {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--accent-dark);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .cp-article-link:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<%= render partial: "layouts/header" %>
<div class="cp-page" id="carpet-cleaning-software">
  <div class="cp-shell">

    <!-- HERO -->
    <section class="cp-hero">
      <div>

        <h1 class="cp-title">
          Manage your <span>carpet cleaning business</span> with <%= ENV['WEBSITE_NAME'] %>.
        </h1>

        <p class="cp-sub">
          <%= ENV['WEBSITE_NAME'] %> is the leading scheduling, planning and invoicing platform for growing carpet cleaning
          businesses. Handle one-off deep cleans and regular maintenance plans – all from a single system.
        </p>

        <p class="cp-hero-tagline">
          The scheduling, planning and invoicing platform built specifically for service teams like yours.
        </p>

        <div class="cp-hero-ctas">
          <a href="/users/sign_up" class="cp-btn cp-btn-primary">Start a free trial</a>
          <a href="/pricing" class="cp-btn cp-btn-secondary">Which plan?</a>
        </div>

        <div class="cp-hero-trust">
          <strong>Trusted by carpet cleaners who want fewer spreadsheets and more booked jobs.</strong>
          <span class="cp-pill">Built for field teams · Works on any device</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Hero media: job board -->
      <div class="cp-hero-media">
        <div class="cp-board">
          <div class="cp-board-inner">
            <div class="cp-board-header">
              <div class="cp-board-header-title">
                Today · Carpet Cleaning
                <span>9 jobs · 3 technicians</span>
              </div>
              <div class="cp-board-filter">View by technician</div>
            </div>

            <div class="cp-board-list">
              <div class="cp-board-row">
                <div><strong>City Centre Offices</strong></div>
                <div>09:00 → 10:30</div>
                <div><div class="cp-status-pill cleaning">In progress</div></div>
              </div>
              <div class="cp-board-row">
                <div>Parkway Apartments – 2 bed</div>
                <div>11:00 → 12:00</div>
                <div><div class="cp-status-pill booked">Booked</div></div>
              </div>
              <div class="cp-board-row">
                <div>Conference Suite · Full clean</div>
                <div>13:30 → 15:30</div>
                <div><div class="cp-status-pill completed">Completed</div></div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="cp-board-footer">
              <span>Send reminders to afternoon customers</span>
              <span><strong>Invoices &amp; payment links</strong> sent automatically</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- INTRO COPY -->
    <section class="cp-section">
      <div class="cp-section-header">
        <p class="cp-section-kicker">For carpet cleaning teams</p>
        <h2 class="cp-section-title"><%= ENV['WEBSITE_NAME'] %> can help your carpet cleaning business grow.</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="cp-body-text">
        <p>
          Whether you’re managing one-off stain removals or routine contracts for offices, hotels and
          landlords, <%= ENV['WEBSITE_NAME'] %> gives you the flexibility you need. Add jobs, reschedule and apply extras
          like upholstery or rug cleaning in seconds – even while you’re on-site.
        </p>
        <p>
          Once a job is complete, generate and send the invoice straight from the app. No paperwork, no
          copying data into separate systems. Your customer gets a professional invoice and secure payment
          options automatically.
        </p>
        <p>
          From the first enquiry to repeat bookings, <%= ENV['WEBSITE_NAME'] %> keeps your team and your clients on the same
          page so you can focus on delivering great results and growing your revenue.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- FEATURES -->
    <section class="cp-section">
      <div class="cp-section-header">
        <p class="cp-section-kicker">Features</p>
        <h2 class="cp-section-title">Let’s explain the features.</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="cp-feature-intro">
        <p>
          <%= ENV['WEBSITE_NAME'] %> is designed to automate your processes and keep admin time to a minimum. It’s easy to
          use on any mobile device, with real-time updates so office staff can keep on top of incoming
          requests and changes to the schedule.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="cp-feature-grid">
        <!-- Manage customer details -->
        <article class="cp-feature-card">
          <p class="cp-feature-label">Customer management</p>
          <h3 class="cp-feature-title">Manage customer details</h3>
          <p class="cp-feature-text">
            Store, access and manage all of your customer and lead information in one place – from property
            access details to preferred products, previous work and pricing.
          </p>
          <div class="cp-feature-pill">Know every customer’s history</div>
        </article>

        <!-- Create & send quotes -->
        <article class="cp-feature-card">
          <p class="cp-feature-label">Quotes</p>
          <h3 class="cp-feature-title">Create &amp; send quotes</h3>
          <p class="cp-feature-text">
            Turn enquiries into booked jobs faster. Build quotes from your price list, send them online for
            approval and convert them into scheduled work with a couple of taps.
          </p>
          <div class="cp-feature-pill">From enquiry to booking</div>
        </article>

        <!-- Appointment reminders -->
        <article class="cp-feature-card">
          <p class="cp-feature-label">Messaging</p>
          <h3 class="cp-feature-title">Send appointment reminders</h3>
          <p class="cp-feature-text">
            Cut down on no-shows and last-minute cancellations with automated SMS and email reminders.
            Configure them to go out before each visit, or whenever makes sense for your customers.
          </p>
          <div class="cp-feature-pill">More completed jobs</div>
        </article>

        <!-- Optimised route navigation -->
        <article class="cp-feature-card">
          <p class="cp-feature-label">Route optimisation</p>
          <h3 class="cp-feature-title">Optimised route navigation</h3>
          <p class="cp-feature-text">
            Reduce drive time between jobs with intelligent routing. Set unique start and end points for
            each technician and let <%= ENV['WEBSITE_NAME'] %> create the most efficient route for the day.
          </p>
          <div class="cp-feature-pill">Less travel, more cleaning</div>
        </article>

        <!-- Marketing campaigns -->
        <article class="cp-feature-card">
          <p class="cp-feature-label">Marketing</p>
          <h3 class="cp-feature-title">Send marketing campaigns</h3>
          <p class="cp-feature-text">
            Build powerful marketing campaigns and send them via SMS or email to customers and prospects.
            Promote seasonal offers, package upgrades or reminder campaigns when it’s time for another
            clean.
          </p>
          <div class="cp-feature-pill">Keep your calendar full</div>
        </article>

        <!-- Email messaging -->
        <article class="cp-feature-card">
          <p class="cp-feature-label">Email</p>
          <h3 class="cp-feature-title">Email messaging</h3>
          <p class="cp-feature-text">
            Use built-in email tools to send booking confirmations, invoices, receipts and follow-ups without
            leaving <%= ENV['WEBSITE_NAME'] %>. Keep a full history of messages alongside each customer record.
          </p>
          <div class="cp-feature-pill">Everything in one system</div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- TESTIMONIALS -->
    <section class="cp-section">
      <div class="cp-section-header">
        <p class="cp-section-kicker">What our customers say</p>
        <h2 class="cp-section-title">See what carpet cleaning businesses think about <%= ENV['WEBSITE_NAME'] %>.</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="cp-testimonial-grid">
        <article class="cp-testimonial-card">
          <div class="cp-testimonial-inner">
            <p class="cp-testimonial-tag">Scheduling &amp; planning</p>
            <p class="cp-testimonial-quote">
              <em>“<%= ENV['WEBSITE_NAME'] %> has evolved into the control centre of our service business.”</em> We plan and
              re-plan daily schedules, send quotes and invoices, and track payments all from one place. Any
              device, any time – it’s essential for any appointment-based team.
            </p>
            <p class="cp-testimonial-name">
              <strong>Chris R.</strong>
              C Rose Cleaning Services
            </p>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="cp-testimonial-card">
          <div class="cp-testimonial-inner">
            <p class="cp-testimonial-tag">Admin &amp; cashflow</p>
            <p class="cp-testimonial-quote">
              “Before <%= ENV['WEBSITE_NAME'] %> we used spreadsheets and paper invoices. Now I just mark jobs as done on my
              phone and invoices are sent automatically. Admin is down, cashflow is up – and my evenings are
              finally free.”
            </p>
            <p class="cp-testimonial-name">
              <strong>Service business owner</strong>
              Carpet &amp; upholstery cleaning company
            </p>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ARTICLES / RESOURCES -->
    <section class="cp-section">
      <div class="cp-section-header">
        <p class="cp-section-kicker">Resources</p>
        <h2 class="cp-section-title">Useful articles to support your carpet cleaning business.</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="cp-articles-grid">
        <article class="cp-article-card">
          <p class="cp-article-tag">Customer story</p>
          <h3 class="cp-article-title">How one carpet cleaner cut admin by 75%</h3>
          <p class="cp-article-text">
            Follow a growing carpet cleaning company as they move from paper diaries and manual invoicing
            to <%= ENV['WEBSITE_NAME'] %>, and see how it changed their day-to-day operations.
          </p>
          <p class="cp-article-meta">Reading time · 6 minutes</p>
          <a href="#" class="cp-article-link">Read more</a>
        </article>

        <article class="cp-article-card">
          <p class="cp-article-tag">How-to</p>
          <h3 class="cp-article-title">Setting up recurring carpet care plans</h3>
          <p class="cp-article-text">
            Learn how to create recurring visits, manage add-on services and keep track of long-term
            maintenance contracts inside <%= ENV['WEBSITE_NAME'] %>.
          </p>
          <p class="cp-article-meta">Reading time · 5 minutes</p>
          <a href="#" class="cp-article-link">Read more</a>
        </article>

        <article class="cp-article-card">
          <p class="cp-article-tag">Growth</p>
          <h3 class="cp-article-title">Marketing ideas for carpet cleaning businesses</h3>
          <p class="cp-article-text">
            Practical tips for filling your calendar using <%= ENV['WEBSITE_NAME'] %>’s marketing tools – from follow-up
            campaigns to seasonal offers and referral requests.
          </p>
          <p class="cp-article-meta">Reading time · 7 minutes</p>
          <a href="#" class="cp-article-link">Read more</a>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

  </div>
</div>
